[h1] Break - vertical spacing

[p] The break tag inserts empty vertical space between elements.

[h2] Default

[code-]
[break]
[-code]

[p] Inserts one line of blank space (10 pixels).

[h2] Custom height

[code-]
[break height=40]
[-code]

[p] The height= value sets the gap size in pixels.

[h2] Example

[code-]
[h2] Section one
[p] Some content here.

[break height=30]

[h2] Section two
[p] More content after a larger gap.
[-code]

